76561197998674122,Not Recommended,410340,19897593,"Posted: 23 December, 2015",all,joshuabardwell,"Video comments are here:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fk2L5Mxe13IThe physics in this game are just not right. The copter is way too floaty. It feels like gravity has been dialed down to 80% or something. Even with the props idle, the copter takes way too long to fall to earth. Doing sharp turns around flags, the copter slides as if it was weightless.The collision model encourages bad habits. You can't just fly through a tree canopy in real life and keep going. Props do not take damage and then ""heal up"". They either break, and you crash, or they don't break.This is an okay video game, but it is a bad simulator. I can't recommend this game at this time (0.2.2) for learning to fly. It will not teach you what it actually feels like to pilot a quadcopter."
